sentences: Alain Goraguer (born 20 August 1931, Rosny-sous-Bois, Seine-Saint-Denis) is a French jazz pianist, sideman of Boris Vian and Serge Gainsbourg, arranger and composer.
He composed for such films as 'La Planète Sauvage' (1973), La Vie de Bohème (1992), Deux jours à tuer (2008) and Saint Laurent (2014).
